incidents.title:
“Dubai Future Solutions – Prototypes for Humanity” advances the first cohort of global ventures into pilot projects and commercialisation in the UAE. The programme is organised under the patronage of Latifa bint Mohammed. Operating from the UAE, Oxara, P-Vita, and Virufy are deploying advanced scientific innovations spanning AI-powered disease monitoring, agricultural biotechnology, and high-efficiency construction materials.
